@startuml
title LibreUni shared agent routing

start
:Read AGENTS.md;
:Read BASELINE.md;
:Read TASKS.md and select packs;

if (Task category) then (course/content)
  :Read GENERAL.md;
  :Read COURSE_STANDARD.md;
  :Read COURSE_WORK.md;
  :Read COURSE_PEDAGOGY.md for authoring or audit;
  :Read COURSE_INTEGRITY.md for content review;
  if (Repair?) then (yes)
    :Read COURSE_REPAIR.md;
  endif
  if (Research or citations?) then (yes)
    :Read RESEARCH.md;
  endif
  if (Interactive component?) then (yes)
    :Read COURSE_COMPONENTS.md;
  endif
elseif (research or explanation)
  :Read RESEARCH.md;
elseif (UI, styling, interaction, a11y)
  :Read UI.md;
elseif (PlantUML)
  :Read PLANTUML.md;
elseif (Agent process or host adapter)
  :Read HOSTS.md;
endif

:Inspect current files and existing changes;
:Edit directly;
:Read relevant agent context for non-trivial work;
:Use VALIDATION.md to run narrowest useful validation;
:Handoff with evidence and update durable context if needed;

stop
@enduml
